author: bmmitch@bellsouth.net
subject: cel gallery
body:
Hey, check out my Lupin cel gallery! I know I'm showing off....but this cel
that I've been waiting since September to get in has finally come (don't
ever order from France) and I needed to show someone else. It's nice, but I
have no idea what episode it's from. I also have no idea which movie my cel
of Lupin with glasses is from, but oh well. Maybe someone else can tell me.
http://members.tripod.com/~ssjvidel/lupin.html
